    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【遊戲內所有人物都在18歲以上】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >注意：此游戏当前不是完整版本，后续将会更新，当前版本为v0.5.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以游玩1-9关</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>右侧面版上有Discord的链接</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家将在游戏中扮演一位炼丹阁楼的掌门人。击败各位女修使她们化为自己的战力</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当然，你也可以与游戏内的女角色互动，在乡间卖货的老板娘，东山的各位女修, 异国的少女...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262320/extras/8ab168c22f4551ce57fd0921b830b6b9.avif?t=1740484944\" width=443 height=797 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你继承了老糊涂师傅遗留下来的炼丹房。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >普通的丹药根本无法用常规材料合成，但是师傅告诉你了一些线索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为何一个山间的炼丹阁里会有养猪房？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为何东山女子频频失踪？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这一切由你来探索。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【角色介绍】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262320/extras/7b2b73f966912c1abd58506c64085dd5.avif?t=1740484944\" width=616 height=274 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【琼华】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>东山的女修士，关卡前的挡门人。</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262320/extras/642d7e158020c598ba7eb7f159bba81d.avif?t=1740484944\" width=616 height=274 /></span><strong><br>【云舒】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>东山的女修士，在东山算是师姐一般的存在。手下拥有众多师妹。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262320/extras/674580f3608acacd746c9fe398327014.avif?t=1740484944\" width=616 height=274 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>【静兰】</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >东山教派的内阁人员，实力在东山是不可忽视的存在。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262320/extras/b67f90f6e5b53038d30bc34709a47846.avif?t=1740484944\" width=616 height=274 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【静姝】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >乡间的货寨的老板娘，样貌美丽的女子为何会在乡下卖货？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由于角色众多无法一一介绍。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【游戏性】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262320/extras/9280738138be1733c2031a757a6ed705.avif?t=1740484944\" width=768 height=1152 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏采用RPG对战的形式，回合制过关。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏进程中你打败的敌人会通过【另类】的形式转化为自己的【战力】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中你还可以种菜，炼丹来提升自己的战力。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262320/extras/48e4d260c71aa2f08012af864928b4b9.avif?t=1740484944\" width=800 height=1052 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将打败东山最后的女魔头</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>在东山成为最强【或者最恶？】的存在！</strong></h2>",
